					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610183402" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;" >Captain Kirby</a></span> <span class="odate time_1526616046 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">18 May 2018 04:00</span>
