			<div class="content" id="post-content-3804029">
									

<p>But its definitely the end of the world.</p>
<p>First article from team &quot;I don't wanna die&quot;.</p>
<p>Thanks to my teammates, as well as Jazstar and DarkStuff for reviewing this!</p>
<p>The gif at the top can be found here: <a href="https://commons.m.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Blender3D_LinearWaveAnim.gif">https://commons.m.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Blender3D_LinearWaveAnim.gif</a></p>
<p>Live long and&#8230; well let's just leave it at that.</p>
<p>If you want to read more stuff by me, you can find it <a href="/captain-kirby-s-personal-file">here!</a></p>

