<p>I'm confused what you mean by this. Are you saying it is boring to read a direct description of a setting? I don't really know how I could've spiced it up without being circuitous, and its only 4 sentences, so its not like that paragraph is very long. Sure, it's not poetry, but I don't understand what makes the opening so boring for you.</p>
